snippet.title: Transformers One | Official Trailer (2024) - Chris Hemsworth, Brian Tyree Henry, Scarlett Johansson
snippet.description:
Every Transformer has an origin. Watch the new trailer for #TransformersOne - only in theatres September 20.

TRANSFORMERS ONE is the untold origin story of Optimus Prime and Megatron, better known as sworn enemies, but once were friends bonded like brothers who changed the fate of Cybertron forever. In the first-ever fully CG-animated Transformers movie, TRANSFORMERS ONE features a star-studded voice cast, including Chris Hemsworth, Brian Tyree Henry, Scarlett Johansson, Keegan-Michael Key, Steve Buscemi with Laurence Fishburne and Jon Hamm.

snippet.title: Trap | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A new M. Night Shyamalan experience. #TrapMovie only in theaters this summer.

Listen to original songs from Saleka as Lady Raven: www.ladyravenmusic.com

Warner Bros. Pictures presents a new experience in the world of M. Night Shayamalan—“Trap” —featuring performances by rising music star Saleka Shyamalan.

A father and teen daughter attend a pop concert, where they realize they’re at the center of a dark and sinister event.

Written and directed by M. Night Shyamalan, “Trap” stars Josh Hartnett, Ariel Donoghue, Saleka Shyamalan, Hayley Mills and Allison Pill. The film is produced by Ashwin Rajan, Marc Bienstock and M. Night Shyamalan. The executive producer is Steven Schneider. 

The director of photography is Sayombhu Mukdeeprom (“Call Me by Your Name”). The production designer is Debbie de Villa (“The Hating Game”). It is edited by Noëmi Preiswerk and the music is by Herdĭs Stefănsdŏttir (“Knock at the Cabin”). The music supervisor is Susan Jacobs (“Old”); the costume designer is Caroline Duncan (“Old”). The casting is by Douglas Aibel (“Asteroid City”).  

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents A Blinding Edge Pictures Production, An M. Night Shyamalan Film: “Trap.” The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on August 9, 2024 and internationally beginning on 1 August, 2024.

snippet.title: All New Atlas | Boston Dynamics
snippet.description:
We are unveiling the next generation of humanoid robots—a fully electric Atlas robot designed for real-world applications. The new Atlas builds on decades of research and furthers our commitment to delivering the most capable, useful mobile robots solving the toughest challenges in industry today: with Spot, with Stretch, and now with Atlas. Stay tuned to see what the world’s most dynamic humanoid robot can really do—in the lab, in the factory, and in our lives.

Read more: https://bostondynamics.com/blog/electric-new-era-for-atlas/

#BostonDynamics

snippet.title: Shannon Sharpe & Chad Johnson react to NBA banning Jontay Porter for life | Nightcap
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Apex Legends: Urban Assault Collection Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch Newcastle and Wraith give you the play-by-play for the Urban Assault Collection Event! 

Gear up, because Three Strikes LTM is back with a vengeance, returning alongside the introduction of an all-new in-game tournament system, Apex Rumble. Enter the Urban Assault Rumble, earning points to climb the leaderboards for glory and rewards! Get Event Offers in the Store, and take down a fresh batch of rewards in the Rewards Track. 

Unlock all 24 limited-time items before the event ends to receive Octane’s Prestige Skin “Apex Riptide”! 

Want to learn more?: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play* battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on PlayStation® 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and PC via EA App and Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Follow us on X: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.
Follow us on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@PLAYAPEX

Production Company: Electronic Arts & Dark Burn Creative
Sound Design and Mix: Respawn Entertainment
All other categories: Electronic Arts & Respawn Entertainment

*Applicable platform account and platform subscription (sold separately) may be required. Persistent internet connection and EA account required. Age restrictions apply. This game includes optional in-game purchases of virtual currency that can be used to acquire virtual in-game items, including a random selection of virtual in-game items."

fr-FR.title: Trailer de l'événement de collection Assaut urbain d'Apex Legends
fr-FR.description:
Regardez Newcastle et Wraith vous dévoiler des informations détaillées sur l'événement de collection Assaut urbain ! 

Équipez-vous soigneusement car le mode Trois chances à durée limitée fait son retour en force simultanément au lancement d'un tout nouveau système de tournoi dans le jeu, l'Affrontement Apex. Prenez part à un affrontement en Assaut urbain, de manière à gagner des points pour grimper au classement en quête de gloire et de récompenses ! Accédez aux offres d'événement dans la Boutique et procurez-vous une nouvelle série de récompenses dans votre suivi de récompenses. 

Débloquez les 24 objets cosmétiques limités avant la fin de l'événement pour recevoir le skin Prestige pour Octane, ""Contre-courant extrême"" ! 

Vous voulez en savoir plus ? http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™ est un jeu de tir Battle Royale Free-to-Play* où des personnages légendaires combattent ensemble aux confins de la Frontière pour la gloire et la fortune. Jouez gratuitement sur PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch et PC via EA app et Steam. http://x.ea.com/57366

Regardez notre chaîne YouTube : http://x.ea.com/56710
Suivez-nous sur X : https://twitter.com/playapex
Suivez-nous sur Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/playapex
Suivez-nous sur TikTok : https://www.tiktok.com/@PLAYAPEX

Production : Electronic Arts & Dark Burn Creative
Conception sonore et mixage : Respawn Entertainment
Autres catégories : Electronic Arts & Respawn Entertainment

* Un compte et un abonnement sur la plateforme applicable (vendus séparément) peuvent être requis. Une connexion Internet permanente et un Compte EA sont requis. Des restrictions d'âge s'appliquent. Ce titre inclut des achats en jeu facultatifs, basés sur un système de monnaie virtuelle pouvant être utilisé pour acquérir des objets virtuels dans le jeu incluant une sélection aléatoire d’objets virtuels.

ko.title: Apex 레전드: 어반 어설트 컬렉션 이벤트 트레일러
ko.description:
뉴캐슬과 레이스의 어반 어설트 컬렉션 이벤트 실황 중계를 시청하세요! 

3 스트라이크 기간 한정 모드가 새로운 게임 내 토너먼트 시스템인 Apex 럼블과 함께 복수를 위해 돌아왔습니다. 어반 어설트 럼블에 참가하여 포인트를 모으고 순위표에 올라 영광과 보상을 획득하세요! 스토어에서 이벤트 오퍼를 확인하고 보상 트랙에서 다양한 보상을 받으세요. 

이벤트가 종료되기 전에 24개의 기간 한정 아이템을 모두 해제하여 옥테인의 프레스티지 스킨 ""Apex 립타이드""를 받으세요! 

자세히 알고 싶으신가요? http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex 레전드™는 레전드 캐릭터들이 프런티어의 변경에서 영광, 명성, 부를 차지하기 위해 치열한 전투를 벌이는 부분 유료* 배틀 로얄 게임입니다. PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, PC EA app, Steam에서 무료로 플레이하세요: http://x.ea.com/57366

YouTube 채널: http://x.ea.com/56710.

Instagram 팔로우: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/
Tik Tok 팔로우: https://www.tiktok.com/@PLAYAPEX

사운드 디자인 및 믹스: Respawn Entertainment
그 외: Electronic Arts, Respawn Entertainment

es-ES.title: Tráiler del evento de colección Asalto urbano de Apex Legends
es-ES.description:
¡Newcastle y Wraith te cuentan todo sobre el evento de colección Asalto urbano! 

Prepárate: el MTL Tres vidas vuelve a lo grande, junto con la presentación de un nuevo sistema de torneos en el juego, Desafíos Apex. ¡Entra en el Desafío de Asalto urbano y gana puntos para ascender en el marcador, alcanzar la gloria y obtener recompensas! Consigue ofertas del evento en la tienda y consigue un nuevo lote de recompensas en el registro de recompensas. 

¡Desbloquea los 24 objetos por tiempo limitado antes de que finalice el evento para recibir el aspecto Prestigio Contracorriente Apex para Octane! 

¿Quieres obtener más información?: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™ es un juego de Battle Royale gratuito* donde personajes legendarios se enfrentan para lograr gloria, fama y fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega gratis ya en PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch™ y PC a través de EA app y Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

Visita nuestro canal de YouTube: http://x.ea.com/56710
Síguenos en X: https://twitter.com/playapex
Síguenos en Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/
Síguenos en TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@PLAYAPEX

Productora: Electronic Arts y Dark Burn Creative
Diseño y mezcla de sonido: Respawn Entertainment
Resto de categorías: Electronic Arts y Respawn Entertainment

Sujeto a restricciones de edad. Este título incluye compras opcionales en el juego de moneda virtual que se puede utilizar para obtener artículos virtuales del juego, incluida una selección aleatoria de los mismos.

ar.title: فيديو دعائي لحدث مجموعة هجوم مدني في Apex Legends
ar.description:
شاهد نيوكاسل وريث يقدمان تعليقاً مفصلاً على حدث مجموعة هجوم مدني! 

استعد، لأن نمط ثلاث ضربات المتاح لفترة محدودة عاد من جديد، وإلى جانبه تقديم نظام البطولات الجديد كلياً داخل اللعبة ""صراع Apex"". اشترك في معركة الهجوم المدني، واربح النقاط للارتقاء في لوحات الصدارة للحصول على المجد والمكافآت! احصل على عروض الحدث من المتجر، واستحوذ على مجموعة جديدة من المكافآت في مسار المكافآت. 

حرّر كل العناصر الأربعة والعشرين المتاحة لفترة محدودة قبل انتهاء الحدث للحصول على مظهر الهيبة ""تيار Apex"" لأوكتان! 

هل تريد معرفة المزيد؟: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™‎ هي لعبة باتل رويال مجانية* حيث تتقاتل شخصيات أسطورية بحثاً عن المجد والشهرة والثروة على أطراف فرونتير. العب بالمجان الآن على PlayStation®4، وPlayStation®5، وXbox One، وXbox Series X|S، وNintendo Switch، والكمبيوتر الشخصي من خلال EA app وSteam‏: http://x.ea.com/57366.

تابعنا على Instagram‏: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.
تابعنا على TikTok‏: https://www.tiktok.com/@PLAYAPEX

شركة الإنتاج: Electronic Arts وDark Burn Creative
تصميم ومزج الأصوات: Respawn Entertainment
كل الفئات الأخرى: Electronic Arts وRespawn Entertainment

*قد يلزم وجود حساب على منصة ملائمة واشتراك على المنصة (يُباع بصورة منفصلة). يلزم وجود اتصال ثابت بالإنترنت وحساب EA. تطبق قيود السن. تشتمل هذه اللعبة على عمليات شراء اختيارية داخل اللعبة للعملة الافتراضية التي يمكن استخدامها للحصول على العناصر الظاهرية داخل اللعبة، بما في ذلك مجموعة عشوائية من العناصر الظاهرية داخل اللعبة.

zh-Hans.title: 《Apex Legends》城市突袭收集活动预告片
zh-Hans.description:

子弹上膛，三次机会限时模式复仇战来了，同时回来的还有全新游戏内锦标赛系统 Apex 乱斗赛。加入城市突袭乱斗赛，赚取积分以登上排行榜，获得荣耀和奖励！在商店中获取活动优惠，到奖励追踪中拿下新一批奖励。

活动结束前解锁全部 24 款限时物品，即可获得动力小子的威望级皮肤“Apex 激流”！

pl.title: Apex Legends – zwiastun wydarzenia kolekcjonerskiego „Miejski szturm”
pl.description:
Newcastle i Wraith pokazują, czego można się spodziewać w wydarzeniu kolekcjonerskim „Miejski szturm”! 

Przygotuj się, ponieważ wraz z wprowadzeniem nowego systemu turniejowego „Rozróba Apex” powraca ograniczony czasowo tryb „Trzy szanse”. Dołącz do „Rozróby miejskiego szturmu”, zdobywaj punkty i pnij się w rankingu, by zyskać chwałę i nagrody! Zdobądź oferty wydarzenia w sklepie i zgarnij nowy zestaw nagród z mapy nagród. 

Odblokuj wszystkie 24 ograniczone czasowo przedmioty przed końcem wydarzenia, by zdobyć prestiżową skórkę Octane’a „Prąd Apex”! 

Chcesz wiedzieć więcej?: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™ to darmowa* gra Battle Royale, w której legendarne postacie mierzą się ze sobą w walce o sławę i chwałę na obrzeżach Kresów. Graj za darmo już teraz na PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch oraz EA app i Steam na PC: http://x.ea.com/57366.

 Wymagane są stałe połączenie z Internetem oraz konto EA.

en.title: Apex Legends: Urban Assault Collection Event Trailer
en.description:
Watch Newcastle and Wraith give you the play-by-play for the Urban Assault Collection Event! 

Gear up, because Three Strikes LTM is back with a vengeance, returning alongside the introduction of an all-new in-game tournament system, Apex Rumble. Enter the Urban Assault Rumble, earning points to climb the leaderboards for glory and rewards! Get Event Offers in the Store, and take down a fresh batch of rewards in the Rewards Track. 

Unlock all 24 limited-time items before the event ends to receive Octane’s Prestige Skin “Apex Riptide”! 

Want to learn more?: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play* battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on PlayStation® 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and PC via EA App and Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.

es-MX.title: Tráiler del evento de colección Asalto urbano de Apex Legends
es-MX.description:
¡Mira a Newcastle y Wraith darte los detalles del evento de colección Asalto urbano! 

Equípate, porque el modo Tres ataques por tiempo limitado regresa con una venganza y con un sistema de torneo completamente nuevo: Contienda Apex. ¡Entra a la contienda del Asalto urbano, gana puntos y sube en la tabla de posiciones por recompensas y gloria! Obtén ofertas del evento en la tienda y consigue un nuevo lote de recompensas en la senda de recompensas. 

¡Desbloquea los 24 objetos por tiempo limitado antes de que termine el evento y recibe el aspecto de prestigio ""Contracorriente Apex"" de Octane! 

¿Quieres saber más?: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™ es un título de juego gratuito* estilo Battle Royale en el que personajes legendarios luchan por la gloria, la fama y la fortuna en los límites de la Frontera. zh-Hant.title: 《Apex 英雄》：城市突擊收藏活動預告片
zh-Hant.description:
觀賞紐卡索和惡靈為城市突擊收藏活動帶來的實況報導！

整裝動作加快，因為復仇心切的三次機會限時模式回來了，這次還加上 Apex 亂鬥賽這個全新遊戲內錦標賽系統聯袂回歸。進入城市突擊亂鬥賽，賺取積分並登上排行榜爭取榮耀和獎勵！在商店中享受活動優惠，並在獎勵路線中取得全新獎勵內容。

ru.title: Apex Legends — трейлер коллекционного события «Городская атака»
ru.description:
Ньюкасл и Рэйф рассказывают о коллекционном событии «Городская атака» прямо с места событий! 

Готовьтесь, потому что временный режим «Три шанса» возвращается, а с ним в игре появится совершенно новая система турниров «Потасовка Apex». Участвуйте в потасовке «Городской атаки», зарабатывайте очки и поднимайтесь по таблице лидеров к наградам и славе! В магазине вас ждут особые предложения события, а в системе отслеживания наград — кое-что новенькое. 

А если откроете все 24 временных предмета внешнего вида до конца события, вы получите престижный облик Октейна «Быстрина Apex»! 

Подробности: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™ — бесплатная игра в жанре «королевская битва», где легендарные персонажи сражаются за славу и богатства на дальних рубежах Фронтира. Играйте бесплатно на PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch и ПК через EA app и Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

ja.title: エーペックスレジェンズ: アーバンアサルト コレクションイベント トレーラー
ja.description:
トレーラーを視聴しよう。アーバンアサルト コレクションイベントについて、ニューキャッスルとレイスが実況で情報を伝えてくれます！

復讐に燃えるスリーストライクLTMが復刻。さらに、新たなゲーム内トーナメントシステム「Apexランブル」が実装されるイベントに向けて準備を整えよう。アーバンアサルトランブルに参戦。ポイントを獲得してランキング上位を目指し、栄光と報酬を手に入れよう！ストア内のイベントオファーを利用し、報酬トラックでは新たな報酬を手に入れよう。

イベントが終了する前に期間限定アイテム全24種をアンロックして、オクタン用プレステージスキン「Apexリップタイド」を受け取ろう！

以下で詳細をチェック: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

pt-BR.title: Trailer do Evento de Coleção Assalto Urbano de Apex Legends
pt-BR.description:
Assista a Newcastle e Wraith comentando cada lance para o Evento de Coleção Assalto Urbano! 

Equipe-se porque o MTL Três Chances está de volta com tudo, e se junta a um novo sistema de torneio no jogo, o Impacto Apex. Entre no Impacto de Assalto Urbano, ganhando pontos para subir no placar em busca de glória e recompensas! Consiga Ofertas do Evento na Loja e receba um novo lote de recompensas na Lista de Recompensas. 

Desbloqueie os 24 itens de tempo limitado antes que o evento termine para receber o Visual de Prestígio ""Correnteza Apex"" do Octane! 

Quer saber mais?: http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event

Apex Legends™ é um jogo gratuito* de battle royale em que personagens lendários lutam por glória, fama e fortuna nos limites da Fronteira. Jogue de graça agora no PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch e PC por meio do EA app e do Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

de-DE.title: Apex Legends: Häuserkampf-Sammlung-Event-Trailer
de-DE.description:
Lasse dir von Newcastle und Wraith das Häuserkampf-Sammlung-Event Schritt für Schritt erklären. 

Wappne dich, denn der befristete Drei-Strikes-Modus kehrt mit dem Wunsch nach Vergeltung zurück und wir führen ein neues Turniersystem namens Apex-Kampf ein. Sammle im Häuserkampf Punkte, um auf der Bestenliste nach oben zu klettern und Ruhm und Belohnungen zu erhalten! Sichere dir im Store Event-Angebote und neue Belohnungen in der Belohnungsreihe. 

Schalte alle 24 befristeten kosmetischen Objekte vor dem Ende des Events frei, um Octanes Prestige-Skin ""Apex-Flut"" zu erhalten!

it.title: Apex Legends: Trailer evento collezione Assalto urbano
it.description:
Newcastle e Wraith ti aspettano con la telecronaca dell'evento collezione Assalto urbano! 

La modalità Tre chance è tornata, stavolta insieme a un nuovissimo sistema di tornei: la Lotta Apex. Iscriviti alla Lotta di Assalto urbano e accumula punti per scalare le classifiche e conquistare la gloria (e un mucchio di ricompense)! Scopri le offerte dell'evento nel negozio, poi completa il contatore premi. 

Sblocca i 24 oggetti cosmetici a tempo limitato della collezione entro la fine dell'evento per ricevere Ondata Estrema, la nuova skin Prestigio di Octane! 

Vuoi saperne di più? Visita http://x.ea.com/apxl/urban-assault-event.

Apex Legends™ è un battle royale gratuito* in cui personaggi leggendari si sfidano per gloria, fama e ricchezza ai margini della Frontiera. Gioca gratis su PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch e PC tramite EA app e Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

snippet.title: F1 24 Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the grid for the season start by pre-ordering EA SPORTS F1® 24 today, arriving May 31 👉 http://x.ea.com/79780 

Be One of the 20 in F1® 24, the official videogame of the 2024 FIA Formula One World Championship™. Get closer to the grid like never before, challenge the legendary Max Verstappen, and take on the greatest drivers in the world.

F1® 23 players can jump into Time Trial challenges using the all-new Alpine, Haas, McLaren, and Williams 2024 team cars by pre-ordering F1® 24 Champions Edition by May 1st.. 

Get all the F1®️ 24 information here 👉 http://x.ea.com/79780 

The digital-exclusive Champions Edition equips you with two new Formula 1® Icons, 18,000 PitCoin, and an F1® World Bumper Pack featuring resources for single and multiplayer gameplay events. Players will also receive up to three days of early access starting May 28, and all pre-orders come with one bonus VIP Podium Pass. 

Players pre-ordering the Standard Edition will receive 5,000 PitCoin and an F1® World Starter Pack.

Subscribe to @EASPORTSF1 for upcoming F1®️ 24 trailers and news.

Follow all the EA SPORTS F1 social channels 👉 https://linktr.ee/easportsf1
 
https://twitter.com/EASPORTSF1 

https://www.instagram.com/EASPORTSF1

"Précommandez EA SPORTS F1® 24 dès aujourd’hui pour rejoindre la grille dès le début de la saison le 31 mai 👉 http://x.ea.com/79780
 
 Faites partie des 20 dans F1® 24, le jeu vidéo officiel du 2024 FIA Formula One World Championship™. Rapprochez-vous de la grille comme jamais auparavant, défiez le légendaire Max Verstappen et affrontez les plus grands pilotes du monde.
 
 Si vous possédez F1® 23, participez à des défis Contre-la-montre avec les toutes nouvelles voitures de la saison 2024 des écuries Alpine, Haas, McLaren et Williams en précommandant F1® 24 Édition Champions d’ici le 1er mai. 
 
 Obtenez toutes les informations sur F1®️ 24 ici 👉 http://x.ea.com/79780 
 
 L’Édition Champions offerte exclusivement en format numérique vous propose deux nouvelles Icônes Formula 1®, 18 000 PitCoin et un pack Pare-chocs F1® World avec des ressources pour les événements solos et multijoueurs. Profitez également de trois jours d’accès anticipé à compter du 28 mai. Toutes les précommandes sont accompagnées d’un Podium Pass VIP en prime. 
 
 Ceux et celles qui précommandent l’Édition Standard recevront 5 000 PitCoin et un pack de démarrage F1® World.

de-DE.title: F1® 24 – Offizieller Reveal Trailer
de-DE.description:

snippet.title: Why A $100,000 Salary Can’t Buy The American Dream
snippet.description:
More than half (52%) of Americans say they would need at least $100,000 a year to be financially comfortable, according to the August 2023 CNBC Your Money Survey. It’s becoming increasingly more difficult to achieve the American Dream, especially as younger generations are beginning their adulthood with thousands of dollars in student loans. Watch the video above to learn more about how much it costs to achieve the American Dream.

it.description:

Il destino ci impone regole crudeli, trasformando il giorno in notte e lasciando spazio al futuro soltanto nel calore persistente dei sogni.
Perciò incrociamo le nostre lame, seppelliamo il bagliore del crepuscolo e accogliamo l'arrivo dell'alba.
E quando la gabbia verrà distrutta...
La fiamma tenue consumerà i fiori non ancora sbocciati e una canzone riecheggierà tra le ceneri.

El destino nos ha fijado reglas crueles, para que el día sea como la noche y que el futuro solo permanezca en el resplandor de un hermoso sueño.
Así que enfrentamos a los demás con nuestras cuchillas, sepultamos el resplandor del atardecer y damos la bienvenida al amanecer.

La suave llama calcina las flores que aún no han florecido, y de las cenizas emana una canción.

ru.title: Анимационный ролик «Горящая в золе песнь» | Genshin Impact
ru.description:
Говорят, взрослеть значит постепенно освобождаться от оков.
Судьба установила для нас жестокие правила, сделав дни чернее ночи, а будущее - отголосками сладких снов.
Поэтому мы, стоя клинком к клинку, хороним последние лучи заката и приветствуем восходящее солнце.
А потом, когда клетка будет разбита...
Пусть ласковое пламя сожжёт нераспустившиеся цветы, пусть раздастся горящая в золе песнь.

ja.title: 【原神】ショートアニメ「燼中歌」（フルver.）
ja.description:
ある者は言う——成長とは、束縛を徐々に解いていく過程だと。
運命は我々に残酷な規則を定めた。それゆえ白昼は黒夜のようになり、未来は美しき夢の余温にしか残らなくなった。
だから我々は刃を交え、落日の残照を埋葬し、朝日を迎える。
そして、籠が破られた時——
優しい炎が蕾を焼き尽くす中、その灰燼に歌声が響き渡ることを願う。

クリーヴ——青戸浩香
クルセビナ——永島由子

fr.title: Genshin Impact - Court métrage : « Une chanson née dans les cendres » (Version complète)
fr.description:
Certains disent que grandir, c'est se libérer progressivement de ses chaînes.
Le destin nous impose des règles cruelles, il transforme le jour en nuit et nous laisse seulement entrevoir l'avenir dans la chaleur persistante des beaux rêves.
Ainsi, nous brandissons nos lames, ensevelissons le soleil couchant et puis accueillons son lever.
Et lorsque la cage se brisera...
Que la douce flamme consume les boutons de fleurs, la chanson résonnera dans les cendres.

Voix :
Clervie : Dawn Bennett
Crucabena : Jennifer Sun Bell
Peruere : Erin Yvette
Directeur des Fatui Pierro, le Fou : Richard Tatum

pt.title: Versão completa do curta-metragem animado de Genshin Impact - "A Canção das Cinzas" #GenshinImpact
pt.description:
Alguns dizem que crescer é um processo gradual de romper as correntes.
O destino nos impõe regras cruéis, transformando o dia em noite e deixando o futuro apenas nos vestígios dos sonhos.
Assim, encaramos uns aos outros, enterramos o crepúsculo e saudamos o nascer do sol.
E então, quando as grades da prisão se quebram...
Que as chamas suaves queimem as flores não desabrochadas, pois até mesmo nas cinzas ecoará uma melodia.

snippet.title: There Are Thousands of Alien Empires in The Milky Way
snippet.description:
Go to https://ground.news/nutshell to get 40% off unlimited access to Ground News so you can compare coverage and think critically about the news you read. 

Get a very special piece of kurzgesagt you can take home (and support our channel in the process!) directly from the kurzgesagt shop here: https://shop.kgs.link/shop-191

Sources & further reading:
https://sites.google.com/view/sources-alien-empire-ocean

We often assume that advanced technology will make it easy for aliens to colonize space. But what if space exploration is always difficult, no matter how advanced you are? 
Let’s travel back in human history, to the colonization of Oceania over 5000 years ago, to find parallels between ancient explorers and extraterrestrial civilizations.

en-GB.title: There Are Thousands of Alien Empires in The Milky Way
en-GB.description:
Go to https://ground.news/nutshell to get 40% off unlimited access to Ground News so you can compare coverage and think critically about the news you read. 

Get a very special piece of kurzgesagt you can take home (and support our channel in the process!) directly from the kurzgesagt shop here: https://shop.kgs.link/shop-191

Sources & further reading:
https://sites.google.com/view/sources-alien-empire-ocean

We often assume that advanced technology will make it easy for aliens to colonize space. But what if space exploration is always difficult, no matter how advanced you are? 
Let’s travel back in human history, to the colonization of Oceania over 5000 years ago, to find parallels between ancient explorers and extraterrestrial civilizations.

snippet.title: MLB Players Try Korean Baseball Stadium Food for the first time!!
snippet.description:
We’re back!! With a very special video today as the LA Dodgers and SD Padres came to Korea to open the season for the first time ever!
We had a chance to meet some of the players and show them some of our favourite iconic Korean Ballpark foods and snacks, in a Baseball Stadium here in Seoul!

We’ve missed you all! We hope you enjoy the video, and stay for tuned next week when we’ll be starting a very exciting new series 👀

--

저희가 돌아왔어요 여러분! 오늘은 특별한 영상을 준비해봤는데요, 얼마 전 사상 최초로 MBL 개막전을 한국에서 열었죠, 그래서 저희가 LA 다저스와 SD파드레스 선수들을 만나고 왔습니다!
선수분들께 대표적인 한국 야구장 음식들을 소개해드렸답니다!

여러분 너무너무 보고싶었어요!! 이번 영상도 재밌게 봐주셨음 좋겠고, 다음 주 부터 정말 야심찬 시리즈가 시작될 예정이니 채널고정 부탁드려요!! 👀

snippet.title: Neil deGrasse Tyson Explains The Three-Body Problem
snippet.description:
What is the three body problem? Neil deGrasse Tyson and comedian Chuck Nice break down why the three body problem is unsolvable and what makes it mathematically chaotic. 

Is the solar system unstable? Find out about Isaac Newton’s worries about the solar system, Pierre-Simon Laplace’s calculus, and perturbation theory. Would a binary star system be chaotic? What about a star system with three suns? Four suns? Five? Learn about the restricted three body problem and how the Jupiter-Earth-Sun system could be chaotic down the line.

Check out our second channel, @StarTalkPlus

Get the NEW StarTalk book, 'To Infinity and Beyond: A Journey of Cosmic Discovery' on Amazon: https://amzn.to/3PL0NFn

Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/startalkradio

FOLLOW or SUBSCRIBE to StarTalk:
Twitter: http://twitter.com/startalkradio
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/StarTalk
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/startalk

About StarTalk: 
Science meets pop culture on StarTalk! Astrophysicist & Hayden Planetarium director Neil deGrasse Tyson, his comic co-hosts, guest celebrities & scientists discuss astronomy, physics, and everything else about life in the universe. Keep Looking Up!

#StarTalk #neildegrassetyson 

00:00 - Introduction: The Three-Body Problem
00:31 - The Chaos in Our Solar System
3:29 - Laplace & A New Branch of Calculus
6:21 - Orbiting Two & Three Suns
8:45 - The Restricted Three-Body Problem
10:09 - Chaotic Systems

snippet.title: 2024 Toyota Land Cruiser Review // Idiot Proof
snippet.description:
The 2024 Toyota Land Cruiser in ‘Land Cruiser’ trim ($61,950 starting in the US, $77,290 starting in Canada) is brand new and now comes standard with a hybrid four-cylinder turbo i-FORCE MAX engine. It’s good for 326 horsepower and 465 lb ft of torque, and comes with many off road goodies like a locking differential, detachable sway bars, and a 2400 watt outlet in the trunk. But where exactly does the Land Cruiser fit into Toyota’s lineup among the 4Runner and the Lexus GX? And does this new hybrid Land Cruiser live up to its reputation of reliability and capability? Thomas and James head to the Algodones Dunes to find out. We hope you enjoy the episode! And then subscribe, silly.

Editor: Karston Chong
Sound: Harrison Dickson and Karston Chong
Magical Genius Logistics Planners: James Engelsman and Joey Alford

snippet.title: Inside Emma Roberts’s Charming Los Angeles Home | Open Door | Architectural Digest
snippet.description:
Today, AD is welcomed by Emma Roberts to tour her charming Los Angeles home. When The ‘American Horror Story’ star and her son moved into their new home, she enlisted AD100’s Pierce & Ward to work their magic on the space. Rich florals and luxurious velvets pair with vintage furniture creating a cozy environment for Roberts to kick back and relax. Roberts was excited at the idea of making her very own grown-up dollhouse and with an extensive doll collection, her home has become just that. Ready for a new chapter in her new home, Roberts couldn’t be happier with how the space turned out. “I have a picture of the day we moved in,” Roberts says, smiling. “I’m holding him and it was the most sunny California day, and we were in front of the blue door of our new house. I just remember feeling like we are exactly where we need to be.”

See more of Emma Roberts's LA home here: https://www.architecturaldigest.com/gallery/step-inside-emma-robertss-la-escape

snippet.title: The Complete FALLOUT Timeline Explained!
snippet.description:
The Fallout franchise has a long and complex history and timeline that has been expanding its post-apocalyptic future ever since the original game’s release back in 1997. With 4 mainline games, a handful of spin-offs, and now a TV show that’s set within the same universe, the series has a big, meaty timeline to wrap your head around. And with the Amazon Prime TV show expanding on the franchise’s lore, and extending the timeline further into the future, there is no better time to dive back into the lore of Fallout than now.

This is the Fallout timeline fully explained.

From the Pre-War origins of RobCo. and Vault-Tec all the way through to Lucy MacLean’s journey to find her father via the stories set in the Capital Wasteland and the Commonwealth, this video breaks down the long and complex timeline of the Fallout franchise.

#TimelineExplained #Fallout #GameSpot

00:00 - INTRO
06:58 - FALLOUT 4 PROLOGUE - 2077
07:51 - FALLOUT (TV) - 2077
08:48 - FALLOUT 76 - 2102
12:09 - FALLOUT - 2161
14:38 - FALLOUT TACTICS - 2197
15:44 - FALLOUT 2 - 2241
18:20 - FALLOUT 3 PROLOGUE - 2258-2274
19:11 - FALLOUT 3 - 2277
25:01 - FALLOUT: NEW VEGAS - 2281
30:27 - FALLOUT 4 - 2287
35:37 - FALLOUT (TV SHOW) - 2296

snippet.title: Connecting Solar to the Grid is Harder Than You Think
snippet.description:
A lot of the interesting challenges with renewables are happening behind the scenes.
🌌Get Nebula using my link for 40% off an annual subscription: https://go.nebula.tv/Practical-Engineering
🎈Watch The Balloon Escape: https://nebula.tv/videos/neo-the-balloon-escape?ref=practical-engineering

We’re in the growing pains stage right now, working out the bugs that these new types of energy generation create, but if you pay attention to what’s happening in the industry, it’s mostly good news. A lot of people from all sides of the industry are working really hard on these engineering challenges so that we’ll soon come out with a more reliable, sustainable, and resilient grid on the other end.

snippet.title: LAKERS at PELICANS | #SoFiPlayIn | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | April 16, 2024
snippet.description:
Never miss a moment with the latest news, trending stories and highlights to bring you closer to your favorite players and teams.
Download now: https://link.nba.com/NBAYouTube

LeBron James (23 points, 9 rebounds, 9 assists), D’Angelo Russell (21 points, 6 assists, 5 3pt. FG), and Anthony Davis (20 points, 15 rebounds, 3 blocks) combine for 64 points to lead the Los Angeles Lakers over the New Orleans Pelicans, 110-106, securing the No. 7 seed in the Western Conference Playoffs. Zion Williamson tallied 40 points, 11 rebounds and 5 assists for the Pelicans. 

The Lakers will face the Denver Nuggets in the first round of the 2024 NBA Playoffs with Game 1 Saturday, April 20, while the Pelicans will face the winner Warriors-Kings for a chance at the No. 8 seed Friday, April 19

Zion Williamson is the first player in Play-In history with at least 40 points, 10 rebounds and 5 assists in a game.

snippet.description:
Get a copy of What If? 2 and Randall’s other books at: https://xkcd.com/books
More serious answers to absurd questions at: https://what-if.xkcd.com/

What would happen if everyone on earth stood as close to each other as they could, jumped, and landed on the ground all at the same instant?

Randall Munroe is the author of the New York Times bestsellers What If? 2, How To, What If?, and Thing Explainer; the science question-and-answer blog What If?; and the popular web comic xkcd (https://xkcd.com). A former NASA roboticist, he left the agency in 2006 to draw comics on the internet full time.

Henry Reich is the creator of MinutePhysics and executive producer of MinuteEarth and MinuteFood and founder of Neptune Studios (the parent company for all three youtube channels).

snippet.title: 2024 Perovskite Breakthroughs are the Future of Solar
snippet.description:
Download Opera for free using https://opr.as/04-Opera-Browser-UndecidedMF  Thanks Opera for sponsoring this video! 2024 Perovskite Breakthroughs are the Future of Solar. Perovskites are often hailed as the next big thing for solar panels. They’re more efficient than silicon PVs could ever be, and they have higher yields. However, their fragility and short lifespans have relegated them to the lab...so far.

But 2024 is looking to be the year of the perovskite. The last few months have seen new perovskite researchers all over the world smashing records, including durability. Because of this, some of these new perovskites are even set to hit the market this year. Let’s check out some of the most exciting breakthroughs in the field and see for ourselves if perovskites are finally ready for their big debut. And why should you care?

de.title: 2024: Perowskit-Durchbrüche sind die Zukunft der Solarenergie
de.description:
Laden Sie Opera kostenlos herunter unter https://opr.as/04-Opera-Browser-UndecidedMF. Danke an Opera für das Sponsoring dieses Videos! Perowskit-Durchbrüche 2024 sind die Zukunft der Solarenergie. Perowskite werden oft als das nächste große Ding für Solarpaneele gepriesen. Sie sind effizienter als Silizium-PV-Module es jemals sein könnten und haben höhere Erträge. Ihre Zerbrechlichkeit und kurze Lebensdauer haben sie jedoch bisher auf das Labor beschränkt... bisher.

Aber 2024 scheint das Jahr des Perowskits zu werden. In den letzten Monaten haben neue Perowskit-Forscher auf der ganzen Welt Rekorde gebrochen, einschließlich der Haltbarkeit. Deshalb sollen einige dieser neuen Perowskite sogar noch dieses Jahr auf den Markt kommen. Lassen Sie uns einige der aufregendsten Durchbrüche in diesem Bereich anschauen und selbst sehen, ob Perowskite endlich bereit für ihren großen Auftritt sind. Und warum sollte Sie das interessieren?

ar.description:

لكن يبدو أن عام 2024 سيكون عام بيروفسكايت. شهدت الأشهر القليلة الماضية باحثين جدد في بيروفسكايت حول العالم يحطمون الأرقام القياسية، بما في ذلك المتانة. وبسبب ذلك، من المتوقع أن بعض هذه البيروفسكايت الجديدة ستدخل السوق هذا العام. دعونا نلقي نظرة على بعض الاختراقات الأكثر إثارة في هذا المجال ونرى بأنفسنا إذا كان بيروفسكايت أخيراً جاهزاً لظهوره الكبير. ولماذا يجب أن يهمك الأمر؟

snippet.title: Devin Haney & Ryan Garcia Have an Epic Conversation | One on One | GQ Sports
snippet.description:
Devin Haney and Ryan Garcia face-off Saturday, April 20 in Brooklyn, New York. Originally, we planned an epic face-to-face conversation with the fighters pre-match, but tensions are so high they wouldn't sit together. Instead, we've got exclusive separate interviews with both. Who has more drip? How long have they been rivals? Why did they agree to this fight? The title-defending lightweight champion Haney and the formidable Garcia offer their predictions for this fight and share some subtle digs about their readiness and strategies.

snippet.title: How will Israel and the US respond to Iran's attack on Israel? | DW News
snippet.description:
An aerial assault was launched by Iran against Israel overnight: The Israeli army says more than 300 missiles and drones were fired. It is the first time Iran has launched a direct military attack on Israel despite decades of hostility. 
There's been calm over Jerusalem and Tel Aviv in the wake of the barrage. Almost all the missiles were intercepted by Israel and the US. The UK and Jordan have also shot down drones. Air raid sirens sounded across Israel. The Iranian Revolutionary Guard says the assault was in retaliation for an attack on its embassy in Syria on April 1st which killed 16 people including several Iranian generals. What considerations will Israel have to take into account as it decides how to respond? How difficult will it be for Israel and the US to agree on a clear response to this attack?
If it decides to retaliate, will Israel be able to drum up enough support? And can it respond without the US' support?

snippet.title: Iran's attack on Israel 'will be met with a response', military chief confirms| ITV News
snippet.description:
Israel’s military chief said it will respond after Iran launched an extensive drone and missile attack on Saturday despite world leaders urging them not to retaliate.

Lt. Gen. Herzi Halevi said that Israel is still considering its steps, but confirmed the Iranian strike “will be met with a response.”

He did not mention when this response could happen.

snippet.title: DEVIN HANEY: MILLION DOLLAZ WORTH OF GAME EPISODE 269
snippet.description:
Devin Haney, a rising star in the world of boxing, returns to the Million Dollaz Worth Of Game podcast with a wealth of experiences to share. Haney’s career has been marked by determination, skill, and a relentless pursuit of excellence. His upcoming bout with Ryan Garcia on April 20, 2024, promises to be a clash of titans, and fans are eagerly awaiting this showdown.

In a recent episode, Haney took listeners on a tour of his opulent Las Vegas property, where he houses an impressive collection of cars valued at over 3 million dollars. Beyond the glitz and glamour, Haney delved into the heart of boxing. He candidly discussed how popularity, rather than pure skill, often dictates who earns the big paychecks in the sport.

But it’s Haney’s unique bond with his father that truly sets him apart. Unlike other father-son duos in boxing, their success hasn’t driven them apart; instead, it has brought them closer. Haney’s admiration for his father’s guidance and unwavering support shines through in every conversation.

Lastly, Haney shared his list of the top 5 boxers in the game today, along with his thoughts on who truly deserves a spot in the boxing Hall of Fame. His insights are a testament to his passion for the sport and his commitment to leaving a lasting legacy.


PRESENTING SPONSORS

New Amsterdam Vodka
Find your wins with New Amsterdam Vodka

snippet.title: BREAKING: Iran launches “mass drone and missile attack” on Israel | BBC News
snippet.description:
In a dramatic escalation of the crisis in the middle east, Iran has launched a mass drone and missile attack on Israel..

Retaliation by Iran has been widely predicted, following an Israeli attack on the Iranian consulate in the Syrian capital Damascus.

Israel says its armed forces are on full alert with air defences prepared and combat planes in the air.

Jordan has declared a state of emergency.   President Biden has returned to the White House for crisis talks with national security advisers.

Ben Brown presents BBC News at Ten reporting by James Landale in Jerusalem and Will Vernon in Washington.

Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1rbfUog

snippet.title: How Mega Minion SAVED Clash Royale
snippet.description:
The mega minion is an important support card that is a staple in many iconic decks. It has a small, but very important role, and it has influenced the game greatly in the past. This is the entire story of the Mega Minion.

Chapters:
=====================================
00:00 Intro
01:25 The Purpose of Mega Minion
03:01 How Mega Minion Initially Influenced The Meta
06:45 Its First Balance Change
08:31 Another Balance Change
09:37 2017
13:17 Why Wasn’t Mega Minion Nerfed Again in 2017?
14:57 2018
17:29 2019
21:01 October 2019 - December 2019
23:32 2020 - 2021
25:22 The Beginning of the Mega Minion’s Downfall
27:40 The Phoenix is Released, Mega Minion is No Longer Viable
31:15 Mega Minion is Still Bad in 2023, So It Gets Its First Buff
32:32 Last Minute Adjustment / How is Mega Minion Doing Today?
34:05 Outro

ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most success clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Thiago Silva and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Fran Kirby and many more. It’s the only channel where you’ll get an authentic look at this great club including memorable nights with world-class heroes such as Peter Osgood, Gianfranco Zola, Frank Lampard, John Terry, Didier Drogba & Eden Hazard.

snippet.description:
Kellogg’s is teaming up with Minecraft ​⁠(@minecraft) to give you FREE Exclusive Character Creator Items to use in game when you buy any participating Kellogg’s cereals like Frosted Flakes, Froot Loops, Apple Jacks and Corn Pops.

Minecraft and Kellogg’s have partnered with the Arbor Day Foundation to build a better and greener world by planting 250,000 trees in forests of great need in the U.S. 
 
Visit https://arborday.org to learn more about the Arbor Day Foundation's tree planting mission.

• Select Kellogg cereals will include a FREE EXCLUSIVE DCL Minecraft Creator item, on specially-marked promotional cereal boxes.
• Get one FREE EXCLUSIVE Minecraft Character Creator item when you purchase any participating Kellogg’s cereal between now and 7/31/2024. Collect all 3 Character Creator items!
• Take a picture of your receipt and upload to https://www.wkkelloggpromotions.com/  (must be 16yrs+ to participate.)
• You can only select the character creator item once (cannot collect the same item more than once, no trading)
• Character Creator Items are exclusive to the U.S. to use in Minecraft game.
• Offer good through Kellogg’s redemption website: https://www.wkkelloggpromotions.com

snippet.title: Two police officers were shot and killed near Syracuse, New York
snippet.description:
SALINA, N.Y. — It is now confirmed that a Syracuse police officer and an Onondaga County Sheriff's Office deputy were shot and killed in Salina Sunday night.

According to Syracuse Police Chief Joseph Cecile, the officer killed was on the job for about three years. Sheriff Toby Shelley described the deputy killed as a seasoned deputy.

 More: https://cnycentral.com/newsletter-daily/active-police-scene-on-darien-drive-in-liverpool#

snippet.title: Can You Beat DARK SOULS 2 With Only Scythes?
snippet.description:
I mean, they were overpowered in Dark Souls 1, surely that trend continued, right?
...guys?

The reaper run continues into Dark Souls 2 as we try to beat all the games bosses, while simultaneously eradicating the world of all NPC life. Place your bets now on whether the bosses or the NPCs were harder.

Can you beat Dark Souls 2 with only Scythes? Time to find out.

|| MUSIC ||
Hyrule Castle Courtyard - Zelda Ocarina of Time
Ruined Paths - Gravity Rush
Town 1 - Eiyuden Chronicle Rising
Goron City - Zelda Ocarina of Time
Praise the Lamb - Cult of the Lamb
Outset Island - Zelda Windwaker
Pond - Bugdom
Rainbow Road - Super Mario Kart
Panic Puppet Zone - Sonic 3D Blast
Katana Zero - Katana Zero
Anchordeep - Cult of the Lamb

snippet.title: Chicago mass shooting: New details released
snippet.description:
Chicago police released new details after a child was killed and 10 other people were wounded at a family gathering on the South Side Saturday night. 

Officers responded to a Shotspotter alert in the 2000 block of West 52nd Street in the Back of the Yards neighborhood at 9:18 p.m. and found several victims with gunshot wounds. 

A witness told police that they saw a black sedan pull up and someone inside fired multiple shots into the crowd before fleeing southbound on Damen Avenue. 

A family was gathered for a birthday party outside when gunmen opened fire with assault rifles and handguns, according to a police report. There were 75 shell casings recovered from the scene, according to the report. The first officers at the scene began lifesaving measures, including applying tourniquets and chest seal bandages.

Subscribe to FOX 10 Phoenix!

snippet.title: I Ran A Custom Croissant Bakery For A Day
snippet.description:
Try Headspace today for free: https://headspace-web.app.link/e/SF Use my code: SAFIYA60 - for a 60-day free trial of the app! Crunchy Quaso sleepcast when??

HELLO FRIENDS!! So, the internet loves croissants. And, coincidentally, so do I. So after falling down a cronut hole of croissant content - I decided, I needed to make some frickin croissants. And surprisingly, Black Box Bakery in Denver agreed to take me on as a pastry apprentice! Not only did I get a high-altitude pastry bootcamp - learning how to laminate my own dough, and roll my own classic croissants - but I also got to create my own custom, semi-goth, cream-filled croissant CUBE - that you can actually try at Black Box Bakery if you go there in person!! What do you think? Beetlejuice or beetleJUICY?

A big thank you to everyone at Black Box Bakery for helping us out with this video; make sure to check them out here! ​​https://www.blackboxbakery.com/
and https://www.instagram.com/blackbox_bakery/

If you’re interested in trying our custom croissant cube for yourself, they will be available Friday, Saturday, & Sunday for the next month! You can either pre-order the Safiya x Black Box Croissant online for pickup here https://order.toasttab.com/online/black-box-bakery-5505-w-20th-ave-unit-182 or visit Black Box Bakery in person while supplies last!

(this video is NOT sponsored by Black Box Bakery and we are not receiving any portion of their sales - they are just a cool small business we love!)

Check out our merch shop here!! https://fiendishbehavior.com 

My Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/safiyany/​
My TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@safiyany
My Snapchat: https://t.snapchat.com/3JJgsbuN
Tyler's channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCc6BTuuTzfMLKj_RgwuDnQw 
Our YouTube Shorts channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLKQoTgt5BwFJJKWyeXHbig 

MUSIC
Via AudioNetwork

Executive Producers: Safiya Nygaard & Tyler Williams
Production Manager / Producer: Melissa Douglas
Junior Associate Producer: Ishara Mathews
Content Promotions & Video Packaging Manager: Alaina Simmons
Editor: Andrew Lainhart
Editor: Mandy Padgett
Editor: Hailey Cox
Graphic Designer: Dayana Espinoza

0:00 Intro
3:52 Off to Denver!
5:16 Mise En Place
7:29 Mixing & Forming Our Dough
10:05 Laminating Our Dough
12:53 Classic Butter Croissant Tutorial
15:47 Making The Viral Mulled Wine Croissant Cube
17:56 Making & Rolling Our Custom Cube
20:47 Making The Fillings For Our Quaso
24:10 Day 2: Baking Day
27:25 Decorating The Mulled Wine Cubes 
29:24 Our Custom Cube Croissant Deco
31:40 Taste Test
35:18 Outro

snippet.title: PESO COMPLETO (Video Oficial) - Peso Pluma, Arcángel
snippet.description:
PESO COMPLETO (Video Oficial) - Peso Pluma, Arcángel
Double P Records©

➸ ESCUCHA / LISTEN: https://orcd.co/n9jvvpq


➸Música 

Interpretación - Peso Pluma, Arcángel
Composición  - Hassan Emilio Kabande Laija,  Austin Santos, Carlos Dominguez Kenzo, Robert Rodriguez DM, Jorge Valdez, Dimelo Flow, Marvin Hawkins, Maff
Producción - Dimelo Flow, Maff


➸Video
Director @fernandolugo @pesopluma 
Creative @johndelacasa @pesopluma 
EP @buenavibra 
Producer @fabi.olive 
Local producer @meganshorttt 
Dop @sidsingh.dp 
PD @kaylinnduffy 
Edit @joanpabon_ 
Color @sidsingh.dp


➸Letra
Papi, oye lo que te voy a decir
Tu dices que tumbo
Si tu dices que el dinero no cambia a las personas
Simplemente no están haciendo dinero

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo chupando
Parecen hookeros
Voy pa’ veinte años dándoles palo
Como un pelotero
Y si me retiro les dejo Austincito 
Y también se jodieron

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo mamando
Parecen hookeros
Desde Jalisco me estoy quedando con el mundo entero
Yo soy artista pero vivo como un capo ranchero

Se juntó Pablo y Gustavo
En una finca contando los chavos
El primo de Peso Pluma
Cabrón yo soy peso pesado
Pa’ lo que roncan de Bravo
Yo me los como y los cago
Tengo una suite en Condado
Cuatro putas que me clavo
En Santurce soy Jordan en Chicago

Pa’ mis hijos las combis son Kith
Ronca y te dejamo’ sin front teeth
A mi siempre se me va la mano
Voy a cambiar mi apellido a Austin Smith

Tengo llena como tres caleta
El dinero se guarda en maletas
Tu me odias a mis tres puñetas
A quién tú se lo mamas a mi me respetas

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo chupando
Parecen hookeros
Voy pa’ 20 años dándole palo
Como pelotero
Y si me retiro les dejo Austincito 
Y también se jodieron

Ando en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo mamando
Parecen hookeros
Desde Jalisco me estoy quedando con el mundo entero
Yo soy artista pero vivo como un capo ranchero

El primero fue Daytona
Nunca tuve fecas
Trabajé mil horas
Que sigan buscando
Pero no tuvieron la escuela de grandes personas
La que se navega, 4.5 llora
El que pegó su propia banda sonora
Ahora varios ya me prenden veladoras
La cuenta la mandan a la contadora
La cadena de infinito nunca se me traba la que traigo al cinto
Superona y 4.5 de Houston hasta Puerto Rico
De México es el chamaquito
Y aquí sigo firme cuento billetitos
Por eso yo nunca me agüito
Ni sufro por ningún culito

Quiero saber si a ustedes
Les gusta la música del señor Santos
El que empezó a hacer trap primero que todos
Este cabrón es un ídolo para mí
Que se escuche fuerte el grito para Arcángel

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo chupando
Parecen hookeros
Voy pa’ 20 años dándole palo
Como pelotero
Y si me retiro les dejo Austincito 
Y también se jodieron

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo mamando
Parecen hookeros
Desde Jalisco me estoy quedando con el mundo entero
Yo soy artista pero vivo como un capo ranchero






Peso Pluma

⋟Spotify - http://bit.ly/435v7ii
⋟TikTok - http://bit.ly/3ZBp3LC
⋟Apple Music - http://bit.ly/411a92p

snippet.title: What Happened To The Nautilus?
snippet.description:
Get Nebula for just $2.50 a month here: https://go.nebula.tv/mustard

Watch More Mustard Videos & Support The Channel: https://nebula.tv/mustard

Thanks to Wesley Dobbs for providing logos on the Russian space mirror!  https://www.artstation.com/kingvangarh

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/MustardChannel
Mustard Merchandise: https://mustardchannel.com/
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/MustardVideos
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Mustard-109952378202335

For centuries, the North Pole remained elusive. Early attempts to reach it were primarily motivated by the search for a navigable route through the Arctic to Asia, known as the Northwest Passage. Later, explorers focused specifically on reaching the Pole itself. But for centuries, reaching it seemed impossible. The polar environment was extremely unforgiving. Located in the middle of the Arctic Ocean, the North Pole is covered by a vast expanse of sea ice which constantly changes due to wind, ocean currents and seasonal melts. Explorers tried to reach the pole using ships, dogsleds, and even traveling by foot. The first verified, and officially recognized expedition to reach the North Pole didn’t occur until 1926 (although several explorers claimed to have reached it earlier). It was first reached using the airship Norge, which flew overhead, but did not land on the surface.  

In the late 1920’s, accomplished explorer Sir Hubert Wilkins became convinced that a submarine would provide the ultimate means of reaching the North Pole. A submarine could travel for extended periods beneath the ice, avoiding the extreme hazards above which had caused earlier expeditions to fail. Carrying the latest scientific equipment, the submarine’s crew could conduct valuable meteorological, oceanographic, biological, magnetic, and spectrographic experiments.

Wilkin’s submarine would be called the Nautilus. It was a retired WW1-era submarine that had been extensively modified by renowned Naval Architect Simon Lake. The Nautilus featured a heavily reinforced bow, a shock absorber and sledge runners to protect it from collision with sea ice. A diving compartment and airlock was also added to allow divers to explore the depths while the submarine remained submerged. Most importantly, the Nautilus was fitted with three ice drills, allowing the submarine to recharge batteries, refresh air and even allow the crew to exit while the submarine still remained below the ice. 

The Nautilus and her crew of 20 men began their expedition to the North Pole in June of 1931. 
None of them realized how grueling their journey would be, and almost immediately things began to go wrong.

snippet.description:
Dear reader, this author must inquire…what is the primary force that guides us on our paths? Is it our minds, or our hearts? Perhaps we should discover the answer together.... Bridgerton Season 3: Part 1 arrives May 16, only on Netflix.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81487890

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 260 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Bridgerton Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Determined to move on from Colin Bridgerton, Penelope Featherington sets out to find a husband, only to receive help from the last person she expects.

snippet.description:
► SUBSCRIBE to the Channel! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYPYEhWUvvKFgmgkLACagXA?sub_confirmation=1

What if the skibidi toilet forces struck down all of the titans until only one remained? In this post-apocalyptic city, the alliance’s final hope is THE LAST TITAN! For the next 100 days I’ll be surviving as the Last Titan in Minecraft, using my incredible powers to take down skibidi toilets and grow into bigger and stronger forms. snippet.title: Carin León - Cuando La Vida Sea Trago [Official Video]
snippet.description:
Carin León - Cuando La Vida Sea Trago [Official Video]

🦁 Suscríbete a mi canal: 
https://n9.cl/kp49a

Escucha "Cuando La Vida Sea Trago" en tu plataforma favorita: 
https://carinleon.lnk.to/CuandoLaVidaSeaTrago

LETRA👇:

Soy el que le sacó canas a mamá
El que siempre soñó con tener lana
Y desde una edad temprana
Siempre tuve esa ambición

Yo soy el dolor de cabeza de las suegras
De la familia soy la oveja negra
De chamaco siempre di problemas y preocupación

Un grosero pero tuve educación
A la escuela sólo iba por la linda del salón
Hubo una que me falló
Desde ahí soy un cabrón
Solamente porque mami me enseñó a pedir perdón

Y que me disculpe la que ofendí por salir mujeriego 
Desde morro me gustó el desmadre
Así soy, no lo niego
Y el que tiene derecho a juzgarme
Lo veo después en el cementerio
Mientras tanto, cuando la vida sea trago
Me la tomo en serio

No vine a ser ejemplo a seguir
Yo soy como soy
Mami quería un buen hombre
Y le salió un bad boy
No me quieran cambiar
Yo estoy bien como estoy
Les duele porque gusto no les doy

No ha llegado una que me enderece
Una se va y me escriben trece
Portarme bien no está en mis intereses
Pico y me voy, después me lo agradeces

Soy bien loco y en eso tienen razón
Puedo querer a muchas, tengo grande el corazón
Agradezco la intención, pero no tengo solución
Y solamente porque mami me enseñó a pedir perdón

Y que me disculpe la que ofendí por salir mujeriego 
Desde morro me gustó el desmadre
Así soy, no lo niego
Y el que tiene derecho a juzgarme
Lo veo después en el cementerio
Mientras tanto, cuando la vida sea trago
Me la tomo en serio

snippet.title: Zach Bryan - 28
snippet.description:
You took a train to the south side of Boston,
You showed me where your old man stayed,
Took 28 years of blood I was lost in,
To feel loved on my own birthday,
I always felt like I’s in between something,
Like home and somewhere far away,
But tonight on the west side in a bar out in Brooklyn,
I saw tears outline your face,

How lucky are we?
It’s been a hell of a week, but we’re all grown now,
There’s smoke seeping out, of your bloody teeth,
But you’re home somehow,

I’ll be upstairs with the guitar I’s given,
When I was barley fourteen,
When did McGlinchey’s get so damn crowded,
And why are the crowds so damn green?
I lost my mind on the streets of the city,
Maybe I lost all hope too,
Took 28 years of blood pumping through me,
To get to this evening with you,

How lucky are we?
It’s been a hell of a week, but we’re all grown now,
There’s smoke seeping out, of your bloody teeth,
But you’re home somehow,

How lucky are we?
It’s been a hell of a week, but we’re all grown now,
There’s smoke seeping out, of your bloody teeth,
But you’re home somehow

snippet.title: Becky G - MERCEDES (Official Video) ft. Oscar Maydon
snippet.description:
Becky G & Oscar Maydon – MERCEDES (Official Video)
 
Music:
Apple Music: https://BeckyG.lnk.to/Mercedes/applemusic
Spotify: https://BeckyG.lnk.to/Mercedes/spotify
Amazon: https://BeckyG.lnk.to/Mercedes/amazonmusicstreaming

Lyrics:
La niña quiere que yo la monte en la mercedes
Yo estoy que me caso por lo rico que se mueve
Y yo que antes solía decir
Mujeriego me voy a morir
Pero a ese culito le doy todo lo que quiere
 
Que te
Parece si nos vamos de una vez
Al cinco estrellas para un TBT
Eres la más bella de las mujeres
 
Si quieres también
Nos destapamos una de Moët
Bebe me encanta tu olor a Chanel
Es una diabla aunque sabe que tiene
Carita de ángel
 
Everyday quiero tenerte para comerte a besos
Yo nunca me había sentido así te lo confieso
Y yo que antes solía decir
Que lo del amor no era pa’ mi
Pero cuando vi tus ojos me olvidé de eso
 
Que te
Parece si nos vamos de una vez
Al cinco estrellas para un TBT
Se que de todas tu a mi me prefieres
 
Si quieres también
Nos destapamos una de Moët
Se que te encanta mi olor a Chanel
Soy una diabla aunque yo se que tengo
Carita de ángel

snippet.title: Zach Bryan - Like Ida
snippet.description:
When you wake in the morning and I’m not by your side,
just know that I’m halfway to Dallas,
I’m stoned out my mind, I’m half buzzed ‘bout full time since you left me to die here last August,
When you make it to Nashville, you can tell by one hat tilt, that that shit just ain’t my scene,
I like out of tune guitars, taking jokes too far and my bartenders extra damn mean, 

So roll where you’re rolling,
I’ll be praying you’re fine,
Wherever you’re going,
Stay walking that line,
‘Cause they’ll eat and they’ll spit ya’,
But you’re not their fool,
They don’t know ya’ like ida,
Back home on barstools,

I’m out on the road, when I’m going I go,
I make music with all of my friends,
I miss your silhouette, catching coastal sunsets,
And the sound of that rusty door hinge,
But that days bound to come when I finish this run,
And I’m rolling right into your arms,
And that bullshit you see on the late night TV
is a long way from our beating hearts, 

So roll where you’re rolling,
I’ll be praying you’re fine,
Go where you’re going,
Stay walking that line,
‘Cause they’ll eat and they’ll spit ya’,
But you ain’t their fool,
They don’t know ya’ like ida,
Back home on barstools,

So roll where you’re rolling,
I’ll be praying you’re fine,
Wherever you’re going,
Stay walking that line,
‘Cause they’ll eat and they’ll spit ya’,
But you ain’t their fool,
They don’t know ya’ like ida,
Back home on barstools

Best guitarist of all time, member of the band: Chris Braun

snippet.title: Season 10: Venture Forth | Overwatch 2 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Overwatch 2  Season 10: Venture Forth launches April 16!

Unlock our new Damage Hero, Venture. Dig into their ability kit and explore new underground mechanics.

Venture and all other Heroes are unlocked immediately for everyone who has completed the new player experience. Venture will also be available in Competitive at launch.

Blur the lines between good and evil with the Mirrorwatch Event, where the virtuous have crumbled into villainy, and the wicked emerge as heroes.

Collect Mythic Prisms as you progress through the Battle Pass and use them to unlock Vengeance Mercy and select previous skins at the Mythic Shop!

Engage in an intense tug of war as you vie for control across a series of capture points in Clash Game Mode Trial, an exciting new 5v5 game mode.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!

_

Estos cabrones los tengo mamando
Parecen hookeros
Desde Jalisco me estoy quedando con el mundo entero
Yo soy artista pero vivo como un capo ranchero

El primero fue Daytona
Nunca tuve fecas
Trabajé mil horas
Que sigan buscando
Pero no tuvieron la escuela de grandes personas
La que se navega, 4.5 llora
El que pegó su propia banda sonora
Ahora varios ya me prenden veladoras
La cuenta la mandan a la contadora
La cadena de infinito nunca se me traba la que traigo al cinto
Superona y 4.5 de Houston hasta Puerto Rico
De México es el chamaquito
Y aquí sigo firme cuento billetitos
Por eso yo nunca me agüito
Ni sufro por ningún culito

Quiero saber si a ustedes
Les gusta la música del señor Santos
El que empezó a hacer trap primero que todos
Este cabrón es un ídolo para mí
Que se escuche fuerte el grito para Arcángel

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo chupando
Parecen hookeros
Voy pa’ 20 años dándole palo
Como pelotero
Y si me retiro les dejo Austincito 
Y también se jodieron

Andamo’ en alta
El Peso con Arca
Vuela dinero
Estos cabrones los tengo mamando
Parecen hookeros
Desde Jalisco me estoy quedando con el mundo entero
Yo soy artista pero vivo como un capo ranchero

snippet.title: Tiger Woods Second Round | Every Single Shot | The Masters
snippet.description:
Every shot from Tiger Woods' second-round 72. #themasters

Since 1934, the Masters Tournament has been home to some of golf’s greatest moments. Amidst blooming azaleas, towering pines and flowering dogwoods, the first full week of April ushers in a stage unique to golf and to sport. Over four days and 72 holes, the smallest field in major championship golf competes for a chance to capture the Green Jacket and a place in Masters history.

---

Softbox Lantern: https://amzn.to/46wtJ9x
Gimbal: https://amzn.to/3ZHgNv5
Camera Bag (for travel): https://amzn.to/46cHdY1

What happened to DOGDAY?!
Dogday is one of the Smiling Critters from Poppy Playtime Chapter 3: Deep Sleep (created by Mob Entertainment). He’s a giant toy dog who was captured by Catnap and imprisoned in a jail cell… and his legs were tragically ripped off. His design and scene in the game is pretty creepy and insane, so after making our DIY animatronic Catnap, we knew a hanging Dog Day animatronic had to be next.

We started by making some fake walls in the style of theatrical flats to act as his jail cell. His frame was made of steel and powered by pneumatics, thanks to the help of Hallucinations Creations who make amazing pneumatic animatronic mechs for the haunted house industry. We used wire, duct tape, and foam to make the shape of his body and covered the whole thing in shaggy fur. His head was custom 3D modeled and 3D printed. The whole thing was animated with a prop controller from Purgatory Props.

We love how our real life DogDay turned out! He’s an awesome pneumatic prop and he's going to make the perfect companion to our growing collection of custom Halloween animatronics like our Catnap, Huggy Wuggy and Springtrap animatronics. Who do you want to see us make next? And where do we put this giant prop now?!

Thanks for watching and Stay Wicked, y’all!

#Animatronics

snippet.title: Dark Matter — Official Trailer | Apple TV+
snippet.description:
There are infinite realities. This is the one where Jason Dessen kidnaps himself. Based on the New York Times bestseller, Dark Matter premieres May 8. https://apple.co/_DarkMatter

Dark Matter is a sci-fi thriller series based on the blockbuster book by acclaimed, bestselling author Blake Crouch. The nine-episode series features an ensemble cast that includes Joel Edgerton, Jennifer Connelly, Alice Braga, Jimmi Simpson, Dayo Okeniyi and Oakes Fegley. Dark Matter makes its global debut on Apple TV+ on May 8, 2024, premiering with the first two episodes, followed by new episodes every Wednesday through June 26.

Hailed as one of the best sci-fi novels of the decade, Dark Matter is a story about the road not taken. The series will follow Jason Dessen (played by Joel Edgerton), a physicist, professor and family man who — one night while walking home on the streets of Chicago — is abducted into an alternate version of his life. Wonder quickly turns to nightmare when he tries to return to his reality amid the mind-bending landscape of lives he could have lived. In this labyrinth of realities, he embarks on a harrowing journey to get back to his true family and save them from the most terrifying, unbeatable foe imaginable: himself.

Crouch serves as executive producer, showrunner, and writer alongside executive producers Matt Tolmach and David Manpearl for Matt Tolmach Productions, and Joel Edgerton. Dark Matter is produced for Apple TV+ by Sony Pictures Television. 

Song: “I Can Never Go Home Anymore” by The Shangri-Las https://music.apple.com/us/album/i-can-never-go-home-anymore/1443845929?i=1443846815

snippet.description:

Lyrics:
It always goes like this
Could’ve predicted it
I’m so naive to think you loved me for me
Kissed as I ran off stage
You’re too old to play this game
Guess you’re still growing up at thirty

Were you surprised by me?
When you took me home
When the glamor wore off
Reduced to skin and bone
I can’t even tell
Who you want to know
I’m a goddess on stage
Human when we’re alone

You took a star to bed
Woke up with me instead
You must have felt so damn deceived
When you 
Made up version of
Me that you thought you’d love
But I am not your Aphrodite

Were you surprised by me?
When you took me home
When the glamor wore off
Reduced to skin and bone
I can’t even tell
Who you want to know
I’m a goddess on stage
And human when we’re alone

You took me for a fool
You stole my youth
You wanted this so much
You watched me rise
Then killed my light
And now you know
I’m not your fucking goddess

I’m no goddess when I’m alone
